Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:01:02.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只為斬斷回歸於無的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:05.03,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}縱使命運有著無限的必然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:07.49,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}仍舊無人知曉明日將在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:10.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}用盡全力掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.20,0:01:14.62,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}將親眼見到的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:17.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:22.72,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Shout out 將自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:25.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}怒吼出來
